nationwide trading of New York Stock Exchange-listed issues, with
788 up, 467 down and 513 unchanged.
   A fire at the Securities Industry Automation Corp. in lower
Manhattan's financial district delayed the usual 9:30 a.m. EST
opening of stock trading. SIAC process trades for the exchanges.
   When activity resumed at 10:30 a.m., prices almost immediately
headed higher.
